quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  43,61,"And most surely it is (the above events or the Quran or he, Jesus) is a sign of the knowledge of coming of the Hour (of Resurrection and Judgment), therefore have no doubt about it and follow Me: this is the Straight Way"
  43,62,And let not the Satan prevent you; surely he is your open enemy
  43,63,"And when Jesus came with clear arguments he said, \"I have come unto you with wisdom, and that I may make clear to you some of that wherein you differ; so be careful of your duty to Allah and obey me"
  43,64,"Surely Allah is my Lord and your Lord, therefore serve Him; this is the right path.\" (See John)"
  43,65,"But parties from among them differed, so woe to those who do wrong because of the chastisement of a painful day"
  43,66,"Do they wait for aught but the Hour, that it should come upon them all of a sudden while they perceive not"
  43,67,"The friends shall on that day be enemies one to another, except those who guard (against evil)"
  43,68,"O My servants! There is no fear for you this day, nor shall you grieve"
  43,69,Those who believed in Our revelations and Surrendered (in Islam)
  43,70,"Enter you the Garden, you and your wives, rejoicing"
  43,71,"There shall be sent round to them golden plates and cups and therein shall be all that their souls desire, and delights the eyes, and you shall abide therein"
  43,72,Such will be the Garden which you are given as an inheritance for what you did
  43,73,For you therein are abundant fruits of which you shall eat with full satisfaction